name: hung out to dry
description: @sianvictoriauk - feeling hung out to dry - signed right bottom corner - Originally a photograph I captured as part of an art & darkroom photography course on the 13th May 2008. I never ended up using the image. But today, 24/05/21 I've recovered it from a CD, edited it in photoshop to be relevant to my feelings past and present and finally get this piece seen.
